p the same API and we avoid breakage.\n","created_at":"2015-07-15T20:23:24.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/6448#issuecomment-121735880","id":121735880,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/6448","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDEyMTczNTg4MA==","updated_at":"2015-07-15T20:23:24.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/121735880","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars0.githubusercontent.com\/u\/97088?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk3MDg4","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"mrdoob","type":"User","id":97088,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/orgs"}},{"index":24,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"few things to note: \n1. Wouldn't MatrixCached and  matrixWorldCached be a better name?? It would also make a lot more clear that they don't get updated a la minute. \n2. This changes the performance charateristics so this should be rather well documented.\n","created_at":"2015-07-16T10:24:45.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/6448#issuecomment-121920540","id":121920540,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/6448","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDEyMTkyMDU0MA==","updated_at":"2015-07-16T10:24:45.0